18:20.100 --> 18:22.820
for a project I'm interested in, knowing

18:22.820 --> 18:25.020
it's going to have a meaningful impact on my users,

18:25.020 --> 18:27.340
knowing that it's being written under my terms

18:27.340 --> 18:29.820
