18:29.820 --> 18:32.380
This isn't a retrospective I wanted to write,

18:32.380 --> 18:34.820
but it's nice to drop the veneer for a few minutes

18:34.820 --> 18:37.180
and share an honest take on what it's like.

18:37.180 --> 18:40.500
