22:11.060 --> 22:12.260
which felt really awesome, too.

22:12.260 --> 22:13.760
So then it was like a double whammy.

22:13.760 --> 22:17.060
And so it felt like it was worth the time,

22:17.060 --> 22:18.660
and it was nice to get a break in the rain.

